title: Hum Hain Kamaal Ke
subTitle: Two men with hearing and speech impairments run a grocery store. When a man is murdered in their store by an underworld gang who are after stolen diamonds, they try their hand at solving the case.

title: Prem Deewane
subTitle: A young couple in love run away together after their parents oppose their relationship. They are misguided into kidnapping a wealthy person for a big ransom by a shrewd uncle who has his own agenda.

title: Raja Ko Rani Se Pyar Ho Gaya
subTitle: A man raised to believe in fairy tales falls in love with a woman he saved from drowning. He goes to great lengths to win the affection of this woman, who he believes to be a mermaid princess.

title: Akbar Birbal
subTitle: Clever Birbal aids Emperor Akbar in witty adventures, solving puzzles and delivering justice across Mughal India, unfolding tales of wisdom and humor.

title: Pralay the Destroyer
subTitle: Some thugs annihilate an entire family and flee the scene without facing any consequences. Years later, the universe balances the scales of justice through the sole survivor of the tragedy.
When mobiles start flying from people's hands, Dr Vaseegaran and his robot Nila are asked to help. However, due to Pakshi Rajan having a hand in this, the two have to reinstate Chitti to defeat him.

title: Krrish
subTitle: After discovering his father's truth, Krrish must reveals his superpowers to the world and becomes the masked superhero.

title: Kisi Ka Bhai Kisi Ki Jaan
subTitle: Bhaijaan, the eldest of three siblings, refuses to get married to maintain harmony in his family. However, complications arise after his brothers conspire for him to fall in love.

title: Tirangaa
subTitle: Brigadier Suryadev Singh and Shivajirao Waghle, a police inspector, work together to track down a terrorist who plans to evade India.

title: Andhaa Kanoon
subTitle: When his parents are killed by three men, Amar, Akbar and Anthony, Vijay teams up with a forest officer who was framed in a murder case to avenge their deaths.

title: Andhaa Kanoon

title: Jai Mahashakti
subTitle: The king of Travancore is ruthless and tortures his subjects. However, Vaikundasamy, an incarnation of Lord Vishnu, decides to put an end to this tyranny.

title: Fox
subTitle: Arjun, an accomplished but corrupt criminal lawyer who has the habit of winning each case he fights, decides to turn over a new leaf. However, soon he is accused of killing five people.

title: P Se PM Tak
subTitle: A poverty-stricken prostitute arrives in the city with the intention to change her life. However, the city's politics interests her and she strives to pursue it professionally.

title: Prithviraj Chauhan
subTitle: Prithviraj Chauhan, a great ruler, strives to overcome multiple challenges in order to defeat his enemies and ensure peace in his kingdom.

title: Khatta Meetha
subTitle: A seemingly corrupt petty contractor faces challenges from the local municipality, his family, his employees, as well as a former girlfriend and her family.

title: Devi
subTitle: Devi, a snake goddess, vows to protect the daughter of the man who died while trying to save her from a powerful demon. However, she falls in love with a human, unaware of the consequences.

title: Pardesi
subTitle: An innocent villager is wrongly sentenced to death for a murder he didn't commit, but a twist of fate and a meeting with his lookalike lead to an unexpected chain of events.

title: Jaan
subTitle: Karan is hired to kill Kajal, the granddaughter of a police commissioner, but they end up falling in love. However, fate tests their bond when Karan's true intentions are revealed.

title: Ghayal
subTitle: Balwant Rai, a corrupt businessman, frames Ajay for the murder of his brother. Later, with no support from those close to him, Ajay takes an unlikely route to seek revenge.

title: Tahqiqaat
subTitle: A young woman's corpse goes missing from the grave and is replaced with the cadaver of a priest. Arun, the priest's brother, decides to solve the mystery of this crime.

title: Tahqiqaat
subTitle: A young woman's corpse goes missing from the grave and is replaced with the cadaver of a priest. Arun, the priest's brother, decides to solve the mystery of this crime.

title: Double Gadbad
subTitle: A series of comical complexities ensue when two men who look alike find themselves in numerous problems, leading to utter confusion.

title: Wah Taj
subTitle: Tukaram Marathe, a farmer from Maharashtra, fights against the government, claiming that the land where the Taj Mahal stands is his.

title: Sri Ram Mandir
subTitle: Gopanna, a devotee of Lord Rama, goes through various trials and tribulations while collecting funds to construct a temple. He receives help from his deity throughout his journey.

title: Gangubai Kathiawadi
subTitle: A woman is forced to abandon her Bollywood dreams after her boyfriend sells her to a brothel. As time passes, she builds strong connections in the criminal underworld and rises to power.

title: Movie
subTitle: Bringing the best in television.

title: Haan Maine Bhi Pyaar Kiya
subTitle: Pooja divorces her husband for being unfaithful and gets a job as secretary to a film star. The two fall in love, before her ex-husband returns and she finds herself confused between the two men.

title: Phool Aur Angaar
subTitle: A young man rescues a woman from being molested but gets accused of the heinous crime instead. Trying to apprehend the miscreants, he gets caught in a web of deception and lies.

title: Raja Ki Aayegi Baraat
subTitle: A woman's desperate plea for justice falls on deaf ears as she's forced against her will to marry the man who assaulted her.

title: Lal Baadshah
subTitle: Lal Singh, a righteous and helpful man, clashes against Dayal Singh, a powerful personality. However, things get complicated when a hidden treasure is involved and Lal's tragic past is disclosed.
